site.about.header.title: ShipHaul Logistics Inc
site.about.header.subtitle: Shaping the Next Generation of Logistics Services
site.about.company.title: The Company
site.about.company.text: Our company, ShipHaul Logistics Inc, was founded and is based in Montréal, Canada. Our services is targeted to be launch in Q4 2020, and we aim to start offering our services in the metropolitan region of Montreal and quickly grow to the rest of Canada and North America.
site.about.mission.title: Our Mission
site.about.mission.text: Freight Transportation is a crucial, but a challenging industry. We aims to provide smart logistics services by combining technology with a connected network of logistics services providers, working together in a smart way to provide a better logistics experience and a more efficient, transparent, safe & secure logistics services, and ready to respond to todays and future freight services demands and requirements.
site.about.values.title: Our Values
site.about.values.text: To commit to our mission, we based our most important values on:
site.about.values.value1: Building a culture of continuous innovation and problem solving.
site.about.values.value2: Building lasting win-win relationships with our partners and customers.
site.about.values.value3: Providing great user experiences and great customer services for our customers and partners.
site.about.values.value4: Creating a culture of excellence, great quality assurance and customer satisfaction in the company and at our suppliers
site.about.research_partners.title: Our Research Partners
site.accurate_eta.text: Get accurate updates of your freight estimated time of delivery so you can know when to expect your shipment.
site.accurate_eta.title: Accurate ETA
site.carrier.features.title: ShipHaul Intelligent Logistics Platform and Network
site.carrier.features.text: ShipHaul helps your book more loads and run your logistics opertions efficiently and with less hassle
site.carrier.advantages.title: The Advantages of joining our Network
site.carrier.advantages.why_join: Our free to join and usage freight services platform allows you to offer your freight services, and manage your team, fleet and freight operations efficiently.
site.carrier.advantages.competitive_adva: Increase your competitive advantages with enhanced freight services and offer added value freight services to your customers.
site.carrier.advantages.full_visibility: Take advantage of the Real-Time Visibility features to provide full shipment visibility, accurate time of arrival to your customers, and enhance your freight operations by tracking all your shipment movements in real time.
site.carrier.advantages.price: Keep control on your freight service rate by submitting manual or automatic quotes to shipment requests. Once the shipment is delivered, you will be paid for your freight services whitin a week.
site.carrier.advantages.management: Our platform let you manage your freigh services, assets, team and documents, and run your freight operations efficiently, helping you increase your fleet utilization, optimize your freight operations, improve your delivery performance and accuracy, get matched to freight service demand that best matches your preferences and capacity, and finally improve your safety and customer satisfaction.
site.carrier.advantages.mobile_app: Our mobile app for drivers, guides the driver through the whole shipment process, providing GPS navigation with truck specific routes and traffic information, and tracks the truck live position.
site.carrier.advantages.text.p2: With the ShipHaul Logistics platform, you would have full control and tranparency on your rates, and you will get paid for your freight services whitin a week.
site.carrier.header.title: The Smart way to Haul
site.carrier.header.subtitle: Whether your company operates one truck or a fleet of trucks, ShipHaul helps you book more Loads, manage your Freight operations efficiently, and enhance your Freight services capabilities.
site.carrier.book_freight.title: Intelligent Load Matching
site.carrier.book_freight.text: ShipHaul's intelligent load matching algorithms helps you find loads that match your company's capacity and preferences, while aiming to optimize your logistics operation efficiency.
site.carrier.freight_management.text: Our Platform let you Manage your freight operations, your team and your assets.

site.carrier.freight_services.title: Book Loads and Manage your Freight Operation Efficiently
site.carrier.full_visibility.title: Real-time insight over freight operations
site.carrier.full_visibility.text: ShipHaul lets you and your customer know where their shipments and assets are in real time and when they are expected to arrive. Moreover, our intelligent system learns from your logistics movements to help your run your logistics operations with better efficiency and adapted to your preference.
site.carrier.intelligence_optimization.t: With real-time insights over freight operations, as well as real-time insight over freight market conditions, ShipHaul Intelligent system learns every second to provide you with intelligent insight for your logistics operations, helping your business improve its efficiency and profitability with less complexity.

site.home.introduction.title: ShipHaul Freight Services Platform
site.home.introduction.text: ShipHaul Logistics Freight Service Platform, can help your company through the whole supply chain logistics process. From planing your shipments, finding the best freight services for your needs, following your shipments in real-time until delivery, preparing and tracking your shipments documents, and providing after delivery support and insights.
site.home.introduction.text2: With proper use of the platform, shippers and carriers, could benefits of the many advantages offered by the platform to improve their logistics efficiency, reduce their cost, improve the quality of freight services, increase their shipments visibility and much more.
site.home.carrier.features.freight_servi: Book Loads that meet your expectations
ShipHaul help you book loads that best matches your preference and capacity, while helping you to maintain an optimal operation.

site.home.carrier.features.payments.text: ShipHaul offers a simple electronic payment system to pay you for your services whithin a week after the delivery confirmation.
site.home.carrier.features.driver_app.ti: A Driver Mobile App for Truck Drivers
site.home.carrier.features.driver_app.te: The ShipHaul Driver Mobile App guides truck drivers through the whole delivery process, proving a nagivational GPS with optimal routes that matches the specifications of the trucks and shipments, while sending real-time information to ShipHaul Service so that you and your customer can track delivery in real-time.
